      • checkScan

        public boolean checkScan()
                  throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        This method checks, if the robot can move to the place he wants to move. It scans in front of itself and it scans in an angle in order to check if it fits thru.
        Returns:
        A boolean. If the robot can fit this method returns true. If not it returns false.
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException
